# Boy-Howdy SELinux file contexts
# No custom file contexts needed — howdy files use standard system types:
#   - PAM module: lib_t (installed to /usr/lib64/security/)
#   - Config: etc_t (installed to /etc/howdy/)
#   - Python sources: lib_t (installed to /usr/lib64/howdy/)
#   - User models: etc_t (installed to /etc/howdy/models/)
